latestIgtvVideos.title: ||two tone eye makeup look||
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
hey girls, here is another makeup video for you 👏🏻
I have done a two tone eye makeup using the basic coloured insta liners from @lakmeindia 
Apart from that, ive kept it minimal. 
Ill mention the products ive used in sequence of their application-
• concealer 
• foundation stick
• contour powder
• setting powder 
• eye shadow palatte (for the base)
• insta liners 
• mascara
• blush and highlighter stick 
• smudge me not lipstick
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Myglamm makeup look.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi guys. 
So this is my ever first Makeup video. I was really insecure about posting it but then why not. 🙆‍♀️
I am not a great makeup expert but yes i am a fast learner though😅 i learn a little each time i apply makeup on my face.
If i can do it, you certainly can ladies 💕
.
So getting back to the video, 
Let me mention the products i have used to create this look. 
This is a simple and subtle look with a some shimmer. 
The products in order are 
1. Cream concealer by Inglot- shade 63

2. Pro stroke brow pencil - Jaquline usa

3. Myglamm Spotlight illuminating liquid - sunkissed shade 
4. Myglamm manish malhotra eyeshadow palatte

5. Myglamm manish malhotra illuminating stick 
6. Myglamm LIT liquid matte lipstick - Stargazer 01 .
.
So how do you think the look is ? 
Do let me know in the comments, it would really mean a lot 🙋🏻‍♀️
.
.
